
2gem :
   same initialization of the gem, with 2 sheets and periodicity

gem :
   same initialization as the gem

munster :
   forcing on the magnetic and/or the fluid velocity.
   this can be at t=0, or through time.

uniform :
   uniform magnetized plasma with protons and alphas that can drift

yaourt :
   2 beams configuration (laser reconnection) that can be non-coplanar
   and/or asymetric

shells :
   2 beams configuration with whatever phi & psi angle

harris :
   the "original" harris sheet with a background

felafel :
   uniform 2d plasma with a strong velocity drift against a wall
